00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:21,260 --> 00:01:28,500
Arsenal Military Academy

3
00:01:29,020 --> 00:01:31,500
Episode 33

4
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,000
The blue one.

5
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,840
Blue.

6
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,039
Blue?

7
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:41,920
The large one at the back.

8
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,640
Awesome.

9
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:43,530
Can you do it?

10
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:50,960
No, sir.

11
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:53,080
There must be a problem with your stall.

12
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:53,920
My lady.

13
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,920
So many people are watching.

14
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,759
And many people

15
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:57,800
played it.

16
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:59,000
There is no problem.

17
00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,759
Right.

18
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:00,600
Sir.

19
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,880
Give us the presents.

20
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:02,920
OK.

21
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,900
So many dolls. Who wants them?

22
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,160
Here. Take it.

23
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:19,220
I want it! I want it!

24
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,079
Take it.

25
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,120
- Give me. - Yours.

26
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:24,520
Take it.

27
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:26,620
Thank you, sir.

28
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,520
Let's go.

29
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,640
Let's go.

30
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:41,520
Sir.

31
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,579
I'll take the rest.

32
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,800
I buy them.

33
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,079
This is not the way I do business.

34
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:48,610
I don't care. I'll buy them.

35
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,800
Why don't you let us in?

36
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,440
We will pay for it.

37
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:55,820
Excuse me. Excuse me.

38
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:56,680
Excuse me.

39
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,400
Right.

40
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,720
I have been here before.

41
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:00,800
Exactly.

42
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,200
This store used to

43
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,600
operate to the public.

44
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:05,000
But several days ago

45
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:07,000
the childe bought this place.

46
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:09,060
So it's a private racecourse now.

47
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,160
Ladies and gentlemen,

48
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:10,880
sorry for that.

49
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:11,620
You can't get in.

50
00:03:11,620 --> 00:03:12,800
Is it a private racecourse?

51
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:15,040
We traveled so far to be here.

52
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,320
Please let us get in.

53
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:17,240
I'm sorry

54
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,280
but I can't.

55
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:20,720
Xiaojun.

56
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,560
If you want to ride horses,

57
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:23,120
I'll take you to ride next time.

58
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,600
Poor bumpkin.

59
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,520
Have you ever

60
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,800
seen a horse?

61
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,130
What did you say?

62
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:33,000
You are deaf at a young age.

63
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,480
So poor.

64
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:35,400
Say it again!

65
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,450
I can repeat it a hundred times.

66
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:38,880
Poor wretch!

67
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,040
Bumpkin!

68
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,240
Bumpkin?

69
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:44,160
You are no better than a whore.

70
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,130
Who do you mean is the whore?

71
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:48,200
Who answered me is whom I meant.

72
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,400
You...

73
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,760
Do you want to fight?

74
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:53,840
You hit her!

75
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:54,860
She started it.

76
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,490
Are you alright?

77
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:58,880
Mr. Song.

78
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:01,200
Who are they standing at the door?

79
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,260
A gang of bumpkins.

80
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:04,000
Why don't you keep the order?

81
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,680
Miss Du.

82
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,640
I'm really sorry.

83
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,160
Mrs. Lu called me and said that

84
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,480
you would come to the racecourse.

85
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:10,010
So we are here to pick you up.

86
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:10,960
Well.

87
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,080
Your red horse

88
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,280
gets so strong.

89
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,240
I have arranged to bathe it.

90
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:15,920
You can ride it

91
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:16,950
in a moment.

92
00:04:17,269 --> 00:04:17,829
Really?

93
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,880
Take me to see it later.

94
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:21,920
Mr. Song.

95
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,160
It is a

96
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,380
private racecourse of my cousin.

97
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,480
The guests here are dignitaries.

98
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,760
Not anyone can come in.

99
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,380
Look outside the door.

100
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,360
So many people are standing there.

101
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,420
It's like a market.

102
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,240
People would sneer at us

103
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:38,360
for our family has no rules.

104
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,600
Don't worry, Miss Du.

105
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,420
I'll handle it right away.

106
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:42,760
Ladies and gentlemen,

107
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:43,720
I'm really sorry.

108
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,260
It is indeed a private racecourse.

109
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,990
We don't receive any customer.

110
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,760
So,

111
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,530
please dismiss and go back.

112
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,240
Xiaojun.

113
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,159
Let's go.

114
00:04:56,260 --> 00:04:57,040
Tan Xiaojun.

115
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,480
Mr. Shen.

116
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,120
What brings you here?

117
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:22,520
I come here to ride horses with classmates.

118
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,440
When we arrived,

119
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,640
they said it was a private racecourse.

120
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:25,720
We are not allowed to get in.

121
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,640
I see.

122
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,080
This is my racecourse.

123
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,340
You won't be rejected.

124
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,560
Tell me in advance

125
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,960
next time before you come.

126
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,200
I'll help you arrange it.

127
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:33,659
Really?

128
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,560
But this lady said

129
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,600
this was their private racecourse.

130
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,640
All those who come here are dignitaries.

131
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,120
It will disgrace you

132
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,040
if we go there.

133
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,360
Cousin.

134
00:05:46,740 --> 00:05:48,470
I am the daughter of Du Yucheng.

135
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,800
You visited my home when you were young.

136
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:53,040
Do you remember we are engaged?

137
00:05:54,820 --> 00:05:57,040
Director Du of the Judicial Bureau?

138
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,600
No. No.

139
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:15,800
Xiaojun.

140
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,760
Who is this?

141
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,720
She is my...

142
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:24,920
my classmate.

143
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:37,560
So lovely.

144
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:39,820
Hello!

145
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,570
My name is Shen Junshan,

146
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,780
Xiaojun's friend.

147
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,000
Hello.

148
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:51,600
I introduced myself.

149
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:52,680
It's your turn.

150
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,920
I... I...

151
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:56,480
My name is...

152
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,920
Her name is Xie Xiang.

153
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,320
She is Xie Liangchen's sister.

154
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:02,120
You should have the impression.

155
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:06,120
Liangchen's sister?

156
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,000
Alright.

157
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,240
Mr. Song.

158
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:11,440
Sir.

159
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:12,880
Lead them in.

160
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,560
Pay attention to safety.

161
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,680
In addition,

162
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,920
bring out my best two horses

163
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:22,240
to Miss Tan and Miss Xie.

164
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,840
Get it, sir.

165
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,440
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

166
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:57,240
Xie Zhipei has two children.

167
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,800
The son is Xie Liangchen.

168
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,840
The daughter is Xie Xiang.

169
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:01,480
The brother is two years elder.

170
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:04,000
Two years ago, Xie Liangchen was enrolled at the Arsenal Military Academy.

171
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:06,680
On the first day of school, he encountered a thief at Shunyuan Railway Station.

172
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,010
The thief was cornered,

173
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,360
and robbed a car.

174
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:11,920
Xie Liangchen was killed by the car on the spot.

175
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,680
His sister Xie Xiang was depressed

176
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,140
and dropped out of school.

177
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,760
There has been no news about her since then.

178
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:23,640
This is Xie Xiang.

179
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,400
Riding is so fun.

180
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:46,410
I didn't expect you to ride so well.

181
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:47,660
You shouldn't say that.

182
00:08:47,660 --> 00:08:48,860
I was nearly exposed.

183
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,160
Someone also said that

184
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,640
you were Xie Liangchen's sister before.

185
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:53,760
No one doubted it.

186
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,290
He won't see it through.

187
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:56,640
Xiaojun.

188
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,200
We should leave.

189
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,880
Can I ride another lap?

190
00:08:58,880 --> 00:08:59,720
Just one lap.

191
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:00,280
I'm going.

192
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,340
Alright. Alright.

193
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,840
Xiang.

194
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:14,720
Be careful!

195
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:30,560
Why don't you ride two more laps?

196
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,080
You ride so well.

197
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:36,050
Did your brother teach you?

198
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,520
Do I look scary?

199
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,210
Why don't you look at me?

200
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:47,800
No.

201
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:51,920
Unless...

202
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,880
you have ulterior motives.

203
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:16,060
This is not the first time we have met, right?

204
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,520
Do you know it?

205
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,290
Do you think you can fool me?

206
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,800
I didn't mean it.

207
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:26,120
I have reasons.

208
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:27,880
Right.

209
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,120
It is the second time we have met.

210
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,880
But you shouldn't pretend to ignore me.

211
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:39,440
Last time when you performed on stage

212
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,720
at Shengping Theater,

213
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,860
I was sitting in the first row.

214
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,330
After the performance,

215
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:46,010
I went to backstage for you.

216
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,680
But I didn't see you.

217
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,880
Did you hide away?

218
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:56,120
I thought Xie Liangchen disguised as a man.

219
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:58,280
I didn't know

220
00:10:58,540 --> 00:10:59,600
he has a twin sister

221
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:01,320
until Huang Song told me.

222
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,320
Really?

223
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:25,880
I don't think

224
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,520
you look like him.

225
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:33,250
You are much prettier than him.

226
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:39,770
We can go out together if you have time.

227
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,080
Alright.

228
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:45,960
In a few days,

229
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:48,600
Xie Liangchen will come to our house for dinner.

230
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,800
You can come with him.

231
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:54,520
It's not allowed to ask for leave in school.

232
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,600
Xinhua Girls' School.

233
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,520
The headmaster is Li Yuankui, right?

234
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,780
I'll help you to ask for leave.

235
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,000
No need.

236
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,480
I can ask for leave on my own.

237
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,880
Can you make it approved?

238
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,040
Yes.

239
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:10,640
Good!

240
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:14,100
I'm looking forward to seeing you and your brother.

241
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,000
Mr. Shen.

242
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,000
Thank you to see us off.

243
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,440
Thank you for your hospitality.

244
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,370
You're welcome.

245
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:25,960
We're leaving.

246
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:28,440
Goodbye.

247
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:29,720
Goodbye.

248
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:34,240
Did you get exposed?

249
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,920
Why are you so sad?

250
00:12:37,540 --> 00:12:39,600
He invited me to his house for dinner.

251
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,200
Isn't it good?

252
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:44,170
He also invited my brother,

253
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:46,240
Xie Liangchen from the AMA.

254
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:50,760
What should you do?

255
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:51,760
I don't know.

256
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,000
It's your fault.

257
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,760
You shouldn't take me to the racecourse.

258
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:56,240
I didn't know it.

259
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:12,440
Now your identity has been exposed.

260
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,960
Now there is a letter.

261
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,540
But the same letter will appear next time.

262
00:13:15,540 --> 00:13:18,000
Now that you have a chance to give up,

263
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:18,960
I think it's better

264
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:19,960
for you to leave.

265
00:13:22,640 --> 00:13:23,520
In a few days,

266
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:26,000
Xie Liangchen will come to our house for dinner.

267
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,200
You can come with him.

268
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,320
Wenzhong.

269
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,200
You are back.

270
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:49,000
Nothing happened in school these two days?

271
00:13:49,280 --> 00:13:49,960
Nothing.

272
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,300
What about Xie Liangchen?

273
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:55,280
Nothing happened to Xie Liangchen either.

274
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:55,880
What's up?

275
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,080
Nothing.

276
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,120
Bye.

277
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:01,180
OK. See you around.

278
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,660
Sergeant Lv saw the letter

279
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:13,520
and did not dispel Xie Liangchen.

280
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:15,530
It seems that he knows about it.

281
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:16,880
Right.

282
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:19,160
If she knows no one

283
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,520
in the school authority,

284
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:23,920
it's impossible for Xie Liangchen, a woman, to pass the checkup.

285
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:26,320
I don't know if Sergeant Guo knows about it.

286
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,120
Sergeant Guo.

287
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,300
Why are you standing here?

288
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:33,380
I want to report something to you.

289
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:34,440
Say it.

290
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,880
Could we go in and talk about it?

291
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:39,080
What I will tell you is serious.

292
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,680
It's fine. Say it.

293
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,640
I found a shocking secret.

