299
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:57,640
So I alleged that she was a woman.

300
00:14:58,560 --> 00:14:59,200
Alright.

301
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:01,820
Anything else?

302
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,000
Nope.

303
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:04,940
OK then. Go for your business.

304
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,840
It seems that Sergeant Lv and Guo

305
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,700
