311
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:44,800
Yeah.

312
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:45,640
Two days ago,

313
00:15:45,640 --> 00:15:47,640
Li Wenzhong also lost his new watch.

314
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:48,760
He deserved it.

315
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:49,920
Who did it?

316
00:15:49,920 --> 00:15:51,400
He was so bold to steal.

317
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:52,800
No matter who he is,

318
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:53,760
if I capture him.

319
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,720
I would beat him to death.

320
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:58,320
How much money have you lost?

321
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,440
All of it.

322
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:03,640
Song.

323
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:05,540
Did you lose anything?

324
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,080
No.

325
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:16,920
Don't eat it. It was dirty.

326
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:17,920
We have so much.

327
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:20,130
What's up? You seem absent.

328
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:45,160
- So strange. - Who could it be?

329
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:47,090
I just got my salary and it was gone.

330
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:48,820
What have you lost?

331
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:49,960
I don't know.

332
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:51,360
It was definitely stolen.

333
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,440
I won't afford the expenses this month.

334
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,720
We have to find it out.

335
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:56,760
Right. I lost money three times a week.

336
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,600
It is definitely not a coincidence.

337
00:16:58,600 --> 00:16:59,730
There must be a thief

338
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:00,820
in this apartment.

339
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,680
I lost twenty yuan last night.

340
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:03,840
I have no money for daily expenses this month.

341
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:05,200
It must be the same thief.

342
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,520
The thief is so odious.

343
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:08,069
He stole things so many times,

344
00:17:08,069 --> 00:17:09,520
and left nothing for us.

345
00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:09,960
So hateful.

346
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,349
The thief must be captured.

347
00:17:11,349 --> 00:17:12,950
Let's report to Sergeant Lv.

348
00:17:13,349 --> 00:17:14,200
When the Sergeant arrives,

349
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:16,060
the thief would already run away.

350
00:17:17,349 --> 00:17:18,550
Do you have any ideas?

351
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,520
Any idea?

352
00:17:21,349 --> 00:17:21,960
Well.

353
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:23,520
We can search it.

354
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,680
Search?

355
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:25,109
Yeah.

356
00:17:25,520 --> 00:17:26,589
What we lost,

357
00:17:26,589 --> 00:17:27,880
the money and watch,

358
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,760
are easy to be transferred away.

359
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:32,000
We can't search anything out

360
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:34,200
since so many days passed.

361
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:35,840
Why did you say it?

362
00:17:35,840 --> 00:17:37,120
Let me finish my words.

363
00:17:38,040 --> 00:17:39,440
He must have waited

364
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:41,800
until the lights were off last night.

365
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:44,200
And he shouldn't have acted until we fell asleep.

366
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:46,200
At that time, the dormitory door was locked.

367
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,800
It was impossible for him to transfer the stolen stuffs.

368
00:17:47,800 --> 00:17:48,240
Right?

369
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:49,440
Right.

370
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:51,570
We found it stolen early this morning.

371
00:17:51,800 --> 00:17:53,640
It was impossible for him to run out

372
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:55,200
because it would provoke our suspicion.

373
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,480
So I alleged that

374
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:58,400
the stolen stuffs are still in the apartment.

375
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,920
We can definitely find them.

376
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,200
It makes sense.

377
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:02,380
Is it right?

378
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,880
We all lost money.

379
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:05,840
Did you lose any other stuff?

380
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,400
We all lost money.

381
00:18:11,520 --> 00:18:13,120
But we all have money with us.

382
00:18:13,340 --> 00:18:14,200
So we can't tell

383
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,700
whether it is the stolen money or not.

384
00:18:16,840 --> 00:18:17,320
Yeah.

385
00:18:17,760 --> 00:18:18,440
Yeah.

386
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,640
I also lost my wallet.

387
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:22,280
If we find out where the wallet is,

388
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:23,480
we can tell who the thief is.

389
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:24,740
Yes. I agree to search.

390
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:26,060
- I agree, too. - Agree.

391
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:27,280
Alright.

392
00:18:27,280 --> 00:18:28,520
Let's search it separately.

393
00:18:28,520 --> 00:18:29,640
Search each room.

394
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:31,040
So I'll take the lead.

395
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,160
Search my room first.

396
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:32,840
Go.

397
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:33,900
Search carefully.

398
00:18:35,620 --> 00:18:36,340
Alright.

399
00:18:36,340 --> 00:18:37,960
Who will search my room?

400
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:38,840
We will go.

401
00:18:38,840 --> 00:18:40,100
- All right. - Let's go.

402
00:18:51,100 --> 00:18:52,230
Where are you going?

403
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:54,560
None of your business.

404
00:18:54,560 --> 00:18:55,760
It's not my business.

405
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:57,200
But I have to suggest you.

406
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:59,400
Don't leave out of sight.

407
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:02,500
Otherwise you will be suspected of booty transfer.

408
00:19:02,560 --> 00:19:03,200
What do you mean?

409
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,400
I mean nothing.

410
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:05,340
I'm going.

411
00:19:05,340 --> 00:19:06,520
Don't be afraid

412
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:08,180
if you didn't steal anything.

413
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,200
Unless

414
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,600
you have

415
00:19:10,600 --> 00:19:12,660
something afraid to be searched out.

416
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:16,040
Gu Yanzhen is sleeping inside.

417
00:19:16,040 --> 00:19:17,160
Go and search it

418
00:19:17,320 --> 00:19:18,080
if you dare to.

419
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:18,810
I don't care.

420
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,160
I find something!

421
00:19:40,080 --> 00:19:40,720
Song.

422
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,440
How do you explain

423
00:19:44,340 --> 00:19:45,160
the money?

424
00:19:45,160 --> 00:19:46,160
Yeah.

425
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,240
Where is my watch?

426
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:48,400
Where's my twenty yuan?

427
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,280
- What about my money? - Where is mine?

428
00:19:49,280 --> 00:19:50,080
Where is mine?

429
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:52,280
It is

430
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,560
all of my money.

431
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:55,520
Your money?

432
00:19:55,800 --> 00:19:57,330
Where did you get the money?

433
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:00,000
What do you mean?

434
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:01,240
I mean what I said.

435
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:03,300
We all know his family is poor.

436
00:20:03,340 --> 00:20:04,940
It's about one hundred yuan.

437
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:06,040
How did he get so much money?

438
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:07,720
Song couldn't steal the money.

439
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:08,200
OK.

440
00:20:08,340 --> 00:20:09,680
I know he couldn't steal the money.

441
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:11,520
But where did the money come from?

442
00:20:11,520 --> 00:20:12,380
Xie Liangchen.

443
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:14,560
We know you are good with Huang Song.

444
00:20:14,560 --> 00:20:16,040
But he has to explain

445
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:17,480
where he got so much money.

446
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:19,240
Why does he have to explain it to you?

447
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,400
If your family is rich,

448
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,100
do you have to explain where the money comes from?

449
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:22,920
It's different.

450
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:24,040
I don't think it's different.

451
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:25,040
Xie Liangchen.

452
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:27,200
Don't talk nonsense.

453
00:20:29,280 --> 00:20:30,940
You said you lost your wallet.

454
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,370
Where is the wallet?

455
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:35,100
Didn't you say we can confirm the thief

456
00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:36,520
by the wallet?

457
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,140
Maybe he threw it away.

458
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:39,220
Where did he throw?

459
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:41,280
If he thought of throwing the wallet away,

460
00:20:41,280 --> 00:20:42,680
how could he have put the money

461
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:43,520
in such an obvious place so that you can find it?

462
00:20:43,520 --> 00:20:44,560
He is silly.

463
00:20:44,560 --> 00:20:45,560
You are much sillier than him.

464
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:46,160
You...

465
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:47,160
Alright.

466
00:20:49,280 --> 00:20:50,340
Stop your quarrel.

467
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:55,140
Liangchen.

468
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:57,360
I don't believe Song

469
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:58,760
is a thief.

470
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:00,560
But Song,

471
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:03,040
if you can't explain

472
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:04,800
where you got the money,

473
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:07,610
they will suspect you definitely.

474
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,040
Do you know what I mean?

475
00:21:09,040 --> 00:21:10,100
Right. Huang Song.

476
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:16,400
All the money

477
00:21:17,100 --> 00:21:18,520
was earned by me.

478
00:21:18,520 --> 00:21:19,380
Did you earn it?

479
00:21:21,640 --> 00:21:22,700
How did you earn it?

480
00:21:22,760 --> 00:21:24,020
Why should he tell you?

481
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:25,760
In my view,

482
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:26,760
you must steal it.

483
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:27,720
Say it again!

484
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:28,340
So what?

485
00:21:28,340 --> 00:21:29,340
Do you want to fight?

486
00:21:29,340 --> 00:21:29,800
Come on.

487
00:21:29,800 --> 00:21:30,640
Let's fight. Come on.

488
00:21:30,640 --> 00:21:31,800
Stop now.

489
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:34,090
What are you arguing about?

490
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:35,280
You disturbed my sleep.

491
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:36,040
Gu Yanzhen.

492
00:21:36,040 --> 00:21:37,170
Do you want to fight?

493
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:42,200
Someone lost money again last night.

494
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:43,100
And we searched out

495
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:44,480
so much money from Huang Song.

496
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:45,340
We asked him how he got it,

497
00:21:45,340 --> 00:21:46,560
but he refused to explain it.

498
00:21:46,560 --> 00:21:47,200
Money?

499
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,800
Isn't this my money?

500
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:53,200
Your money?

501
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:55,340
Yes. The money I gave him.

502
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:56,980
The money you gave him?

503
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:58,700
Why did you give him money?

504
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:00,960
Do you defend him

505
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:02,800
as Xie Liangchen did?

506
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:03,920
Yeah.

507
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,400
Didn't you tell them?

508
00:22:10,100 --> 00:22:12,560
Xie Liangchen fought with me two days ago.

509
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:14,240
She was angry with me,

510
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,200
and wanted to change the dormitory.

511
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:18,340
Huang Song agreed but I didn't agree.

512
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:20,500
So I stealthily gave him the money

513
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:23,680
and told him not to change the dormitory with Xie Liangchen.

514
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:24,760
It's so simple.

515
00:22:27,800 --> 00:22:28,840
You are lying.

516
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:31,040
I have no reason to lie. Right?

517
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:33,340
We just asked him where the money was from.

518
00:22:33,340 --> 00:22:34,540
Why didn't he tell us?

519
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:36,440
Yeah.

520
00:22:36,440 --> 00:22:37,240
Why?

521
00:22:37,240 --> 00:22:38,640
Why didn't you tell them?

522
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,800
You are afraid that Xie Liangchen

523
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:47,360
would be angry at it. Right?

524
00:22:49,340 --> 00:22:50,120
Don't worry.

525
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:52,800
I have reconciled with her.

526
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:54,560
She won't change her dormitory.

527
00:22:54,560 --> 00:22:55,120
Right?

528
00:23:18,520 --> 00:23:20,520
What on earth are you hiding from me?

529
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:29,040
What Gu Yanzhen said

530
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:30,530
was fake. Right?

531
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:37,600
Does the money

532
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,640
have anything to do

533
00:23:40,640 --> 00:23:41,770
with your injuries?

534
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,040
I know.

535
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:53,640
Why didn't you tell us about it?

536
00:24:07,340 --> 00:24:09,200
Since you have the reasons for it,

537
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:10,100
forget it.

538
00:24:11,340 --> 00:24:12,600
Be careful these days.

539
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:14,360
This matter was possibly

540
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:16,520
plotted by Li Wenzhong.

541
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:42,060
Huang Song.

542
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:46,040
Gu Yanzhen.

543
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,960
Come. Let's talk.

544
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:05,480
The dormitory doors are all closed.

545
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:06,920
Why don't you go back?

546
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:09,860
Don't you know the way to go in?

547
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:12,760
How do you know it?

548
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:14,820
Of course I know it.

549
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:16,960
You can't fool me by your tricks.

550
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:21,520
Gu Yanzhen.

551
00:25:22,040 --> 00:25:23,770
Thank you for helping me today.

552
00:25:24,100 --> 00:25:26,300
I will pay the money back to you someday.

553
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,080
No need.

554
00:25:27,080 --> 00:25:28,680
It's not concerned with you.

555
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,040
Anyway,

556
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:31,680
you helped me today.

557
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:37,880
Since you know I helped you,

558
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:40,080
I have some words to you.

559
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:42,920
I don't care to pay more money to compensate their losses.

560
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:44,760
Compared with friendship,

561
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:46,290
money is nothing at all.

562
00:25:47,040 --> 00:25:48,400
I have no interest in

563
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:50,280
what you did

564
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:52,200
and how you got the money.

565
00:25:53,040 --> 00:25:53,560
But I know,

566
00:25:53,560 --> 00:25:55,560
you would rather be wronged of theft

567
00:25:55,760 --> 00:25:57,600
than tell the truth.

568
00:25:58,440 --> 00:26:00,770
