569
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:02,100
Once it is revealed,

570
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:06,010
the consequences could be much more serious than steal.

571
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:07,520
Am I right?

572
00:26:10,320 --> 00:26:11,100
Huang Song.

573
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:14,180
Everything has the limit.

574
00:26:15,080 --> 00:26:16,960
Now you are being targeted.

575
00:26:18,040 --> 00:26:19,400
You should stop it

576
00:26:20,020 --> 00:26:22,100
before it's out of control.

577
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:27,880
You know.

578
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:29,840
Money is

579
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:31,240
nothing for me.

580
00:26:37,800 --> 00:26:39,520
I can even deal with officials

581
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:41,600
in the name of my father.

582
00:26:43,600 --> 00:26:44,320
Tell me.

583
00:26:44,560 --> 00:26:46,040
Who did you offend?

584
00:26:46,320 --> 00:26:47,920
